sequenceDiagram
    participant Citizen
    participant CitizenPortal
    participant EvidenceIngestion
    participant IdentityResolution
    participant SemanticTranslation
    participant AwardCalculation
    participant InvestigationQueue
    participant Notification

    Citizen->>CitizenPortal: Submit UC Application
    CitizenPortal->>EvidenceIngestion: POST /evidence/document (passport, payslips)
    EvidenceIngestion->>EvidenceIngestion: Extract assertions from documents
    EvidenceIngestion->>IdentityResolution: POST /identity/cluster
    IdentityResolution->>IdentityResolution: Create new identity cluster (low confidence)
    IdentityResolution-->>EvidenceIngestion: cluster_id, confidence: 0.3
    
    Note over IdentityResolution: Confidence too low for award
    EvidenceIngestion->>InvestigationQueue: POST /investigations/create (identity verification required)
    InvestigationQueue->>Notification: POST /notifications/send (request additional evidence)
    Notification->>Citizen: Additional evidence required
    
    Citizen->>CitizenPortal: Submit bank statements, employer letter
    CitizenPortal->>EvidenceIngestion: POST /evidence/document
    EvidenceIngestion->>IdentityResolution: Update cluster with new evidence
    IdentityResolution->>IdentityResolution: Increase confidence to 0.85
    IdentityResolution-->>AwardCalculation: High confidence identity cluster
    
    AwardCalculation->>SemanticTranslation: POST /semantic/translate (for UC context)
    SemanticTranslation-->>AwardCalculation: Translated evidence attributes
    AwardCalculation->>AwardCalculation: Calculate UC entitlement
    AwardCalculation->>Notification: POST /notifications/send (award approved)
    Notification->>Citizen: UC Award Approved: Â£180.50/week
